---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-brand-50/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-charcoal">
        How Innov-8 works
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
        We sit between you and your field agencies, replacing fragmented supplier management
        with a single technology-enabled relationship.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connection line -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-24 left-[calc(12.5%+20px)] right-[calc(12.5%+20px)] h-0.5 bg-brand-200"></div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 relative z-10">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Receive</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Your case files are ingested, validated, and enriched with address verification and third-party data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 relative z-10">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Allocate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Cases are distributed to the best-performing agencies using data-driven allocation based on geography, capacity, and track record.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 relative z-10">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Track</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Every case progresses through a defined lifecycle. Real-time dashboards give you full visibility from allocation through to completion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 relative z-10">
            4
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Optimise</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Performance is scored and ranked. Top agencies earn more work. Underperformers are replaced. Standards rise continuously.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
